snippet.title: Mulaka: Origin Tribes - Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description:
This is the official Kickstarter trailer for Mulaka, an action-adventure game developed by Lienzo, an independent game development studio in Mexico, inspired by the legends and myths of the Tarahumara culture.

Support our Kickstarter: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/lienzo/mulaka-origin-tribes
